      <div>
        <p class="section-overline">About Huffman Corporation</p>
        <h2 class="section-h2">Built on Honesty and Integrity</h2>
        <div class="about-body">
          <p>Over the last 37 years, Huffman Corporation has earned the respect of the construction industry in and around Bridgeport, West Virginia. Our philosophy is straightforward: give every client the best building experience they have ever had.</p>
